This product includes or may include static aviation and map datasets used for route visualization.

Third-party data notes:

- Airport coordinate data is derived from public airport data provided by OurAirports. Thanks to OurAirports for maintaining this public aviation dataset: https://ourairports.com/
- World coastline / boundary line data is intended to be derived from Natural Earth-style public map data. Review the current Natural Earth terms and attribution expectations before redistributing generated GeoJSON assets in a public release.
- Browser barcode decoding uses @zxing/browser (MIT License) and the bundled @zxing/library (Apache License 2.0). The generated browser bundle is copied into assets/vendor/ during build and is not committed as source.

